here inserted and comming between? Pheu, pheu.

14. Besides, other Functions of what kinde soe're, have for most part, their set places of meeting and dispatch;
〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , Demost. Orat. pro Coron.
〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , Basilicas, Praetoria, guild or common-halls purposely ordain'd to this use; Now is the Ministeriall Function (objectively) the highest of all others: And what congruity in reason can there bee to deny unto it being the highest, that which we carefully provide for, and willingly allow to other far meaner performances?

